    Iterable<PhysicalOperator>, GraphValue<PhysicalOperator>, DbGroupScan, FragmentLeaf, GroupScan, HasAffinity, IndexGroupScan, Leaf, PhysicalOperator, Scan

    public class RestrictedJsonTableGroupScan
extends JsonTableGroupScan
    A RestrictedJsonTableGroupScan encapsulates (along with a subscan) the functionality for doing restricted (i.e skip) scan rather than sequential scan. The skipping is based on a supplied set of row keys (primary keys) from a join operator.
